Heat the oil in a pan, add the onion and saut√© for 3-4 minutes, or until softened.Add the sweetcorn kernels to the pan and cook for 1-2 minutes.Add the cream, saffron and cod pieces and simmer for 2-3 minutes, or until the cod is cooked through.Add the tomato and parsley, season well with salt and freshly ground black pepper and stir.To serve, pour the chowder into a serving bowl and top with the bacon.